## 7.3 Energy Balance

### 7.3.1 Power Generation

**Total Power Generation Capacity:**

```
Solar: 1.2kW (peak) Wind
power: 0.4kW (rated) Tidal
power: 0.2kW (rated)
↓
Total: 1.8kW (theoretical peak)
```

**Average Power:**

```
太陽光：200W（年平均、稼働率17%）
風力 ：120W（年平均、稼働率30%）
潮力 ：140W（年平均、稼働率70%）
↓
合計 ：460W
```

**Daily Power Generation:**

```
460W × 24h = 11.04 kWh/日
```

### 7.3.2 Consumption

**Breakdown:**

```
Compressor: 5kW × Operating time
control system: 50W × 24h = 1.2 kWh/day
Telecommunications system: 20W × 24h = 0.5 kWh/day
Others: 30W × 24h = 0.7 kWh/day
↓
Basic consumption (non-compressor): 2.4 kWh/day
```

**Compressor Operating Time:**

```
Surplus generation: 11.04 - 2.4 = 8.64 kWh/day
↓
Compressor operating time:
8.64 kWh / 5 kW = 1.73 h/day
↓
Approx. 1.7 hours/day
```

### 7.3.3 Duty Cycle Control

**Issue:**

```
I want to
drive continuously ↓
but 1.7 hours/day is not enough
```

**Solution: Intermittent Operation**

```
Pattern 1: Short time intensive
operation: 30 minutes ON pause
: 30 minutes OFF
↓
Actual operation: 12 hours/day (50% duty)
↓
Consumption: 5kW × 6h = 30 kWh/day
↓
Insufficient: 30 - 11.04 = 18.96 kWh/day
↓
impossible
```

**Pattern 2: Long-Term Dispersion**

```
Operation: 1 hour ON Stop
: 2 hours OFF
↓
Cycle: 3 hours
↓
1 day: 24h / 3h = 8 cycles
↓
Actual operation: 8 hours / day (33% duty)
↓
Consumption: 5kW × 8h = 40 kWh/day
↓
Insufficient: 40 - 11.04 = 28.96 kWh/day
↓
Still insufficient
```

**Pattern 3: Utilization of storage batteries**

```
Sunny weather:
High power generation → Compressor running for a long time → Storage battery charging

Cloudy weather and night:
Low power generation → Battery discharge → Short operation of the compressor

In bad weather:
Extremely small power generation → Compressor shutdown → Storage battery preservation
↓
3-day average balance
```

**Optimal Driving Pattern:**

```
Sunny day:
Compressor: 4 hours of operation (20 kWh consumption)
Power generation: 15 kWh
Basic consumption: 2.4 kWh
↓
Surplus: 15 - 20 - 2.4 = -7.4 kWh
↓
Replenishment from storage battery

Cloudy weather:
Compressor: 2 hours of operation (10 kWh)
Power generation: 8 kWh
Basic consumption: 2.4 kWh
↓
Surplus: 8 - 10 - 2.4 = -4.4 kWh
↓
Replenishment from storage battery

Bad weather days:
Compressor: Stop
power generation: 3 kWh
Basic consumption: 2.4 kWh
↓
Surplus: 3 - 2.4 = +0.6 kWh
↓
Charge
to storage battery ↓
Balanced on weekly average
```

### 7.3.4 Improvement Options

**Solar Panel Area Expansion:**

```
6m² → 12m² (2x)
↓
Output: 2.4kW → Average 400W
↓
Daily power generation: +9.6 kWh
↓
Leeway
```

**High-Efficiency Compressors:**

```
Current: 5kW
Improved model: 3.5kW (30% reduction)
↓
Reduced power consumption with the same air volume
```

**Wave Power Addition:**

```
Using
the vertical movement of the floating body ↓
Additional output: 50-100W average
↓
slightly increasing but accumulating
```

