## 10.8 Intellectual Property Strategy

### 10.8.1 Open Source Scope

**Intellectual Property to Disclose:**

```
- Basic blueprint
- Outline of
manufacturing method - Performance evaluation method
- Operational know-how
↓
Available to anyone
↓
Rapid dissemination
```

**Intellectual Property Companies Can Protect:**

```
- Specific manufacturing technology (know-how)
- Unique formulation
of materials - Details of
control algorithms - Design
↓
Promoting
competition among companies ↓
Accelerating innovation
```

### 10.8.2 Patents for Defense

**Objective:**

```
Preventing
malicious patent acquisition ↓
Publishing and patenting
basic technologies first ↓
Licensing royalty-free immediately
↓
No one can monopolize
↓
Protecting an open environment
```

