Approximately
280
ppm

**Present (2025):**

```
425-430 ppm
↓
From pre-industrial times: +145-150 ppm,
1.5 times the natural range: in just 275
years```

### Abnormal growth rate

**Natural Rate of Change:**

Glacial
→ Interglacial (100 ppm increase): Approximately 5,000-10,000 years
↓
Increase rate: 0.01-0.02 ppm/
year

**Rate of anthropogenic change**

From
the Industrial Revolution to the present (150 ppm increase): Approximately 275 years
↓
Rate of increase: Approximately 0.5 ppm/year (initial)
↓
Present: 2-3 ppm/year
↓
100-300 times the natural
rate

