CO2 emissions over the past 20-30 years have not
yet
been reflected in the climate system
. They will
become apparent over the next 20-30 years
.
Even if CO2 emissions were reduced to zero today
,
an additional 0.3-0.5°C of warming would be unavoidable
.

**current situation:**


Current: +1.5°C
Promised warming: +0.3-0.5°C
↓
