Disaster damage reduction: $300 billion/year
Fishing income increase: $50 billion/year
Agricultural income increase: $100 billion/year ↓
Total
: $1,250 billion/year
↓
Payback period: about 4 years (!)
```

**Note:**
This figure only includes benefits that can be monetized. The
figure would be even greater if values ​​such as comfort, health, and biodiversity were included.

