- Operational know-how ↓
Available
to everyone
↓
Rapid dissemination```

**IP that companies can protect:**


- Specific manufacturing techniques (know-how) -
Unique material blending
- Detailed control algorithms
- Design
↓
Promoting competition between companies
↓
Accelerating innovation
```

### 10.8.2 Defensive patents

**the purpose:**

Prevent malicious
patent acquisition
↓
Disclose and patent basic technology first
↓
License it immediately royalty-free
↓
No one can monopolize it
↓
Protect an open
environment```

