↓
Total: $5 million

[Private donations]
Environmental foundation, wealthy individuals
↓
Crowdfunding
↓
Total: $3 million

[Corporate investment] Investment in technology development for
renewable energy companies, shipbuilding companies, etc. ↓ Total: $2 million ↓ Target achieved```






