↓
Ocean Breathing System attracts attention as a solution
↓
Strengthening government support
↓ Accelerating
deployment```

### 11.9.3 Technological innovation

Advances in related
technologies:
- Improved solar cell efficiency
- Decreasing battery costs
- Development of AI and IoT
↓
Improved system performance
↓
Improved economic efficiency
↓
Accelerated
adoption

### 11.9.4 Social Pressure

Frequent climate
disasters
↓
