13.6 Personal Aspirations

### 13.6.1 Transcending Helplessness

Common Feelings:


"I can't do anything alone." "
The problem is too big."
"I'm powerless."
↓
But
```

**The integrated system shows:**

```
Even individuals can:
- Start a green roof
- Compost food waste
- Harvest rainwater
