14.4 Overcoming Barriers

### 14.4.1 Psychological Barriers

**"It doesn't concern me"**

No
, climate change affects everyone , including you and your children
.










**"I'm powerless on my own"**

You
may be small on your own
,
but
you
're not powerless
.
Your actions
will
move others
and
create ripples
.

**"It's too late now."**

No
, there
's
still time.
If
we act between 2025 and 2030
, we'll be
in time for 2050. It's too early to give up .





**"Someone will do it"**


That "someone" is you .
We all need to be "someone. "






### 14.4.2 Practical Barriers

**"I don't have any money"**

It 's
true that an initial investment is necessary
,
but
:
- Energy conservation reduces electricity bills
- Composting reduces fertilizer costs
- Bicycles reduce transportation costs
-
It's beneficial in the long run
- There are
also subsidies and support programs available
.


**"I don't have time"**


I understand you're busy ,
but
it 's a matter of priorities
. Is there anything more important than the future of the Earth ? Also , you don't need a big chunk of time . You can do it in your daily life .












**"I don't know what to do"**

This paper
shows the Ocean Breathing System,
an urban environment improvement system. Specific methods are available . All you have to do is implement it.









-----

14.5 Reaffirming Urgency

### 14.5.1 Countdown

November
2025 (now)
↓ Until
2030: Approximately 5 years
↓
1,825 days
↓
43,800 hours
↓
Every day↓ is
↓
precious
↓
cannot be wasted```

### 14.5.2 Irreversibility

Once
we pass the tipping point
, there's
no going back.
If
the Greenland ice sheet starts to melt
,
it won't stop for hundreds or even thousands of years
. If
the Amazon becomes savanna , it won't return to its original state as a tropical rainforest . Therefore, we must stop it before it passes the tipping point .









### 14.5.3 The cruelty of time lag


Even if we reduce emissions to zero today, global warming will continue for the
next
20-30 years
. This
means that what happens in 2050 will depend on our actions between 2020 and 2030 , so we need to act now .









