[Environment]
Temperature: +2.5-3°C or more
Ocean: Widespread dead zone
Cities: Scorching heat, expanding uninhabitable areas
Biodiversity: Mass extinction in progress

[Society]
Climate refugees: hundreds of millions
Conflict: intensifying conflict over resources
Cities: dysfunctional
Culture: survival comes first, everything else comes second

[Economy]
Economic collapse: partial
unemployment: mass
infrastructure collapse:
chaos: spreading

[People]
Health: Deterioration (heat waves, hunger, disease)
Community: Collapse
Quality of life: Decline
Hope: Loss
↓
This
↓
must be avoided
`````

