↓
A symbiotic
relationship```

### 15.3.3 Energy

**2050 Energy System:**

```
[Power source mix]
Solar: 40%
Wind: 30%
Hydro: 15%
Geothermal, tidal, biomass: 10%
Nuclear (fourth generation, improved safety): 5%
Fossil fuels: 0% (phase-out complete)
↓
100% carbon-free

[System]
- Distributed power generation
- Smart grid
- Energy storage system (battery, hydrogen, etc.)
- Supply and demand optimization (AI control)
↓
Stable supply
↓
Resilience

[Society]
- Energy self-sufficiency (regional and individual levels)
- Local production and consumption of electricity
- Energy democracy
↓
From dependence to
independence```

### 15.3.4 Food

**Food system in 2050:**

```
[Production]
- Circular agriculture (no chemical fertilizers)
- Urban agriculture (rooftop gardens, vertical farming)
- Sustainable fishing (resource recovery)
- Cultured meat and alternative proteins
↓
Diverse production

[Distribution]
- Local production for local consumption
- Reduce food miles
- Reduce distribution losses
↓
Efficient

[Consumption]
- Food waste: almost zero
- Increase in plant-based foods
- Proper nutritional balance
↓
Healthy

[Circulation]
- Food waste: Composting and biogasification
- Nutrient circulation
↓
Complete
circulation```

### 15.3.5 Society

