```
[Values]
Consumption → Circulation
Ownership → Sharing
Competition → Collaborative
Growth → Sustainability
Individualism → Community
↓
Shift in values

[Workstyle]
- Green jobs becoming mainstream
- Breaking away from long working hours
- Work-life balance
- Working in the local community
↓
Working in a humane way

