15.5 A new image of humanity

### 15.5.1 Homo Sustainability (Sustainable Man)

**Traditional Homo Economicus (Economic Man):**

Characteristics
:
- Selfish
- Rational (short-term)
- Profit maximization
- Competition
↓
However:
- Environmental damage
- Social conflict -
Unsustainable

**New Homo Sustainability:**

