A.1.1 Overall Dimensions

"`
[Upper Pyramid (above water)]
Height: 2.0 m
Base: 3.0 m x 3.0 m
Height above water: 1.0 m

[Central core (buoyant body)]
Diameter: 1.5 m
Total length: 3.0 m
Above water: 1.0 m
Under water: 2.0 m

Lower Pyramid (underwater):
Main pipe length: 250 m
Pipe diameter: inner diameter 15 cm, outer diameter 18 cm
Spiral nozzle length: 1.0 m

Total weight:
Dry weight: Approx. 800 kg
Operating weight: Approx. 1,200 kg (including water and equipment)

[Buoyancy]
Total buoyancy: Approximately 2,000 kg
Safety factor: Approximately 200
%

A.1.2 Photovoltaic power generation system


Panel Specifications
: Type: Monocrystalline silicon;
Conversion efficiency: 20%;
Area: 4 panels x 1.5 m² = 6 m²; Nominal
output: 1,200 W (STC);
Operating voltage: 48 V;
Operating current: 25 A

[Output characteristics]
Fine weather: 1,200 W
, Cloudy weather: 300-600 W,
Rainy weather: 50-150 W
, Nighttime: 0 W

[Annual power generation]
Sunshine hours (equivalent): Average 4 hours/day
Annual power generation: 1,752 kWh
Average output: 200 W
```

