Turbine specifications: Type
: Savonius type (vertical shaft)
; Diameter: 0.5 m
; Height: 1.0 m
; Number of turbines: 4;
Material: Aluminum alloy + carbon fiber

[Output characteristics]
Cut-in wind speed: 2 m/s
Rated wind speed: 10 m/s
Rated output: 100 W/unit x 4 = 400 W
Maximum output: 150 W/unit x 4 = 600 W

[Annual power generation]
Average wind speed: 3 m/s (assumed offshore)
Operation rate: 30%
Annual power generation: 1,051 kWh
Average output: 120 W
```

