Turbine specifications: Type
: Darrieus type (oval beater)
Diameter: 0.8 m
Number of blades: 3
Number of bases: 4
Material: Carbon fiber reinforced resin

[Output characteristics]
Cut-in flow velocity: 0.2 m/s
Rated flow velocity: 1.0 m/s
Rated output: 50 W/unit x 4 = 200 W

[Annual power generation]
Average current speed: 0.3 m/s
Operating rate: 70% (ocean currents are relatively stable)
Annual power generation: 1,226 kWh
Average output: 140 W
```

